name: @zodiac/lang-item
description: Core definitions of zodiac lang items
author: James Salas <j@jamesbs.com>

scripts.build: grpc_tools_node_protoc --proto_path=./src --js_out=import_style=commonjs,binary:./src --ts_out=./src --grpc_out=./src --plugin=protoc-gen-ts=./node_modules/.bin/protoc-gen-ts --plugin=protoc-gen-grpc=`which grpc_tools_node_protoc_plugin` id.proto example.proto lang-item.proto lang-item-service.proto
